<p class="sqsrte-large">Trailer Frames</p><p class="">One of the most important parts of your teardrop build is the trailer frame. You want a strong foundation that can take you wherever you want to wander. Unfortunately, finding a quality trailer frame can also be one of the trickiest parts of the build process. </p><p class="">Upon popular request, we now supply <a href="https://wandertears.com/trailer-frames">steel trailer frames</a> for DIYers! A few of DIYers have already picked up their frames from us for their builds, and we can’t wait to see their progress! Just like our teardrops, frames can be customized to meet your vision. From a basic frame to a fully off-road with wheels to match your vehicle.</p><p class="">All trailer frames come with a VIN, Bill of Sale, and Certificate of Origin which will make your life much easier when it comes time to register your teardrop. </p>


















  

    
  
    

      

      
