<h3>Rent</h3><p class="">Wander Tears now has two trailers for rent! We have our personal Vaga model and a Renegade model available. This is the perfect opportunity if you are considering building or buying a teardrop but want to try one out first, or if you’re just looking to have a heck of a time camping in a tiny trailer! And, it comes with <strong>UNLIMITED MILES</strong>! So you can use a teardrop camper the way it’s meant to be used. Check out the details <a href="https://wandertears.com/rent">here</a>!</p><p class="">That is all we have for this months update! We hope you have an awesome March! I can’t believe it’s already halfway over! Now go make tons of progress on your teardrop build, and spend plenty of time outdoors!</p>




