<p class="">We are excited to feature Eric and Nancy, and their DIY build! Eric and Nacy live in Puerto Ricco and have been working on their teardrop trailer in the evenings over the past few months while using the Vaga DIY plans. Eric and his brother have been handling the building, then it will be time to tag Nancy in for the decorating! </p><p data-rte-preserve-empty="true" class=""></p>


















  

    
  
    

      

      
