              <img class="thumb-image" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5f997a4773370b1d7864046d/06fe68c9-c3c4-411a-bb76-9338f0132ca0/Charlie+DIY+Teardrop+Build" data-image-dimensions="1152x1152" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="DIY Teardrop Trailer Build Ireland" data-load="false" data-image-id="61fabbcdff181f7f3a36f9f7" data-type="image" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5f997a4773370b1d7864046d/06fe68c9-c3c4-411a-bb76-9338f0132ca0/Charlie+DIY+Teardrop+Build?format=1000w" />
            
          
        
