<p class="">Not sure what <a href="https://wandertears.com/diy-plans">model</a> your person wants to build and don’t want to ruin the surprise? We have <a href="https://wandertears.com/diy-plans/p/gift-card">gift cards</a> available so you can still get the discounted price!</p><p class=""><br></p><h3>Gifts for Her</h3>


















  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
            "
        >
          
        
        

        
          
            
          
            
              <img class="thumb-image" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5f997a4773370b1d7864046d/4612cc2a-f295-4f44-9147-36d07c0f99b0/Polaroid+camera" data-image-dimensions="3024x4032" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="" data-load="false" data-image-id="61fc02c5d0100b7c9d2e25a0" data-type="image" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5f997a4773370b1d7864046d/4612cc2a-f295-4f44-9147-36d07c0f99b0/Polaroid+camera?format=1000w" />
            
          
        
          
        

        
      
        </figure>
      

    
  


  





<p class="sqsrte-large">Polaroid Camera</p><p class=""><a href="https://amzn.to/3IUVeh6">Polaroid cameras</a> are just plain nostalgic fun! Camping, hiking, and traveling is all about living in the moment. What’s more in the moment than taking a picture and immediately having a tangible picture? </p><p class="">Unlike our phones and digital cameras with seemingly endless storage and do-overs, there’s something special about a one and done, printed shot that captures memories.</p><p class="sqsrte-large"><br><br>Pendleton Blanket</p><p class="">These high-quality blankets are the perfect to throw in the car to go camping for the weekend.&nbsp;<a href="https://amzn.to/3oktjzb">Pendleton Blankets</a> can get up there in price, but if you’re anything like us, you know the value in good quality gear that is going to last for years to come.</p><p class="">Not only are they cozy and warm, but it also makes a great photo prop! Your outdoorsy lady will be ecstatic to get this gift for Valentines day! Here is <a href="https://amzn.to/3ggaARd">our favorite print</a>, and <a href="https://amzn.to/3ojelJI">one</a> that is a little smaller and easier on the budget.</p>


















  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
            "
        >
          
        
        

        
          
            
          
            
              <img class="thumb-image" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5f997a4773370b1d7864046d/0fd2958b-613d-4ab3-874c-540ad6f99e77/hydro+flask+bottles" data-image-dimensions="3024x4032" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="" data-load="false" data-image-id="61fc031914afdc6be4b42b78" data-type="image" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5f997a4773370b1d7864046d/0fd2958b-613d-4ab3-874c-540ad6f99e77/hydro+flask+bottles?format=1000w" />
            
          
        
          
        

        
      
        </figure>
      

    
  


  





<p data-rte-preserve-empty="true" class="sqsrte-large"></p><p class="sqsrte-large">Hydroflask Water Bottle</p><p class="">The amount of <a href="https://amzn.to/3HpCMga">Hydroflask</a> products we own is borderline absurd. But there’s a reason we love this quality brand!</p><p class="">Whether you get a <a href="https://amzn.to/3rjuIbl">giant bottle</a> for road trips, a <a href="https://amzn.to/3glN5Gl">light weight</a> one for hiking, <a href="https://amzn.to/3L1fI9X">coffee cups</a>, a <a href="https://amzn.to/3onT0in">tumbler</a>, or <a href="https://amzn.to/3rjuZen">wine bottle</a> with some matching <a href="https://amzn.to/35yUBeG">wine glasses</a>, you really can’t go wrong.</p><p class=""><br></p><p class="sqsrte-large">ENO Double Nest Hammock + Stand</p><p class="">If she doesn’t have a <a href="https://amzn.to/3HsVeob">hammock</a> yet, you have to get her one! I’ve had the same <a href="https://amzn.to/3AU43Fh">ENO double nest</a> for at least 10 years. Does it have a few burn holes from campfires? Absolutely. But it its such high quality and has come on every camping trip I’ve been on since I got it.</p>


















  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
            "
        >
          
        
        

        
          
            
          
            
              <img class="thumb-image" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5f997a4773370b1d7864046d/4bcf90df-146d-461d-aa44-637e4be4e3b6/IMG_9216.jpg" data-image-dimensions="4000x6000" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="" data-load="false" data-image-id="61fc05a77a964212d75c0d0a" data-type="image" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5f997a4773370b1d7864046d/4bcf90df-146d-461d-aa44-637e4be4e3b6/IMG_9216.jpg?format=1000w" />
            
          
        
          
        

        
      
        </figure>
      

    
  


  





<p class="">If you frequently camp in the desert or on the coast where there aren’t a ton of trees available for hammock hanging, get her a <a href="https://amzn.to/3J6L0ul">hammock stand</a>. We purchased one from <a href="https://www.walmart.com/ip/Ozark-Trail-128-Portable-Steel-Hammock-Stand-Grey-Color/446714067?adid=22222222277446714067_117755028669_12420145346&amp;gclid=CjwKCAiAl-6PBhBCEiwAc2GOVMCeYAflU0MFBYecPaouxjSAXpmhlW_TV5W00hfJtAckkaZYyLvx6hoCz4EQAvD_BwE&amp;gclsrc=aw.ds&amp;selectedSellerId=0&amp;veh=sem_LIA&amp;wl0=&amp;wl1=g&amp;wl10=8175035&amp;wl11=local&amp;wl12=446714067&amp;wl13=6576&amp;wl13=6576&amp;wl2=c&amp;wl3=501107745824&amp;wl4=pla-293946777986&amp;wl5=9010693&amp;wl6=&amp;wl7=&amp;wl8=&amp;wl9=pla&amp;wmlspartner=wlpa&amp;wmlspartner=wmtlabs">Walmart</a> mid cross country road trip last year because I wanted to cuddle while star gazing and we only had single camp chairs. Man is it a game changer! Incredible for stargazing, staying so much warmer, and now you can hammock literally anywhere!</p><p data-rte-preserve-empty="true" class="sqsrte-large"></p><p class="sqsrte-large"><br>Experience Gifts</p><p class="">Okay, so this is my personal favorite. We prioritize experiences together over any tangible gift. Packing up our teardrop for the weekend to a new destination is one of our favorite activities. Here are a few experience ideas that are sure to make the day extra memorable. (Bonus points if they are a surprise!)</p><p class=""><strong>Pack a Picnic</strong></p><p class="">Pack her favorite meal and head to your local park. Everyone loves surprises, picnics and if she’s an outdoor lover you know shell love spending time outside with you.</p><p class=""><strong>Weekend Getaway</strong></p><p class="">Valentines day falls on a Monday, which means the weekend before is the perfect time to head to a new or favorite destination together and soak in the quality time. We suggest a romanic cabin somewhere in the wood with a hot tub….</p>


















  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
            "
        >
          
        
        

        
          
            
          
            
              <img class="thumb-image" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5f997a4773370b1d7864046d/0e9f5567-7aff-40be-86b0-8e20dd73e374/IMG_2234.jpg" data-image-dimensions="2500x2770" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="" data-load="false" data-image-id="61fc07644b6c7f5336322383" data-type="image" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5f997a4773370b1d7864046d/0e9f5567-7aff-40be-86b0-8e20dd73e374/IMG_2234.jpg?format=1000w" />
            
          
        
          
        

        
      
        </figure>
      

    
  


  





<p class=""><strong>Sunrise (or Sunset) Hike</strong></p><p class="">If you have an outdoorsy woman in your life, I guarantee she loves a good sunrise and sunset. Pack her favorite coffee (or wine), some snacks for the top, and surprise her with an outdoor adventure she is sure to love!</p><p class=""><strong>Rent a Camper</strong></p><p class="">Thinking about building or buying a travel trailer of your own? Check out <a href="https://www.outdoorsy.com/rv-search?address=Aiken%2C%20South%20Carolina%2C%20United%20States&amp;page%5Boffset%5D=0">Outdoorsy</a>, <a href="https://www.rvezy.com?gclid=CjwKCAiAl-6PBhBCEiwAc2GOVLVqchyeQM5WvHKWmHaZK142OciUrBzBH5KyZ2IhMjL7uvezn-usNhoCTh4QAvD_BwE&amp;hsa_acc=131-823-3223&amp;hsa_ad=519895708003&amp;hsa_cam=12360386280&amp;hsa_grp=123255107698&amp;hsa_kw&amp;hsa_mt&amp;hsa_net=adwords&amp;hsa_src=g&amp;hsa_tgt=dsa-1255109671325&amp;hsa_ver=3&amp;rvz_adgroup=123255107698&amp;rvz_camp_id=12360386280&amp;rvz_campaign=12360386280&amp;rvz_content&amp;rvz_term=519895708003&amp;utm_campaign=12360386280&amp;utm_device=c&amp;utm_feeditemid&amp;utm_medium=ppc&amp;utm_source=google&amp;utm_term=519895708003">RVeasy</a>, and <a href="https://rvshare.com">RVshare</a> for something you may be interested in and test it out for the weekend! There’s no better way to know what you want and need on the road than experiencing it. </p><p data-rte-preserve-empty="true" class=""></p><p class="">We hope your Valentines day (and every day for that matter) are filled with love, adventure, and the great outdoors! </p><p class="">Follow <a href="https://www.instagram.com/wandertears/">Wander Tears</a> for teardrop trailer tips, build tutorials, our favorite gear, and daily adventure inspiration.</p>




