<p class="sqsrte-large">Social Media</p><p class="">We took a little intermission from posting on <a href="https://www.youtube.com/c/WanderTears">YouTube</a>, but we're back baby! The Renegade LT build (<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?t=104s&amp;v=gXTIuKnI-BY">Part 1</a> and <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?t=48s&amp;v=UoKeTKQ5pK0">Part 2</a>) are now live! We will be posting new videos every other week and working our way up to posting every week. If there is anything specific you would like to see, let us know!</p><p class="">For daily build tips, travel inspiration, and helpful videos + photos, make sure you follow us on <a href="https://www.instagram.com/wandertears/?hl=en">Instagram</a> and <a href="https://www.facebook.com/wandertears">Facebook</a>.</p><h3>Rent</h3><p class="">We have officially started renting two Wander Tears Trailers! We have our personal Vaga model and a Renegade model for rent. This is the perfect opportunity if you are considering building or buying a teardrop but want to try one out first, or if you’re just looking to have a heck of a time camping in a tiny trailer! And, it comes with <strong>UNLIMITED MILES</strong>! So you can use a teardrop camper the way it’s meant to be used. Check out the details <a href="https://wandertears.com/rent">here</a>!</p>


















  

    
  
    

      

      
