<p data-rte-preserve-empty="true" class=""></p><p class="">For his exterior, Brad went with a beautiful wood varnish finish. He used fiberglass, epoxy, and spar varnish to get his ending look. What do you think?</p><p class="">To follow along with Brad and Sabrina, follow their account <a href="https://www.instagram.com/bradanselmo/">@bradanselmo</a> on Instagram!</p>




