<h4>Tell us about the cot and how you came up with that idea.</h4><p class="">I stumbled upon a photo of a cot in a teardrop and immediately asked Danny if we could make it happen. I’m so glad he was able to find space for it. This made the camper so much more functional for us and added years of use. We chose a cot vs. a permanent bunk so that it could be rolled away when we’re not using it or if the kids aren’t with us!</p>









  
    
      

        

        
          
            
