  <blockquote data-animation-role="quote"
  >
    <span>&#147;</span>Use the weekend to build the life you want, not trying to escape the life you have.<span>&#148;</span>
  </blockquote>
  <figcaption class="source">&mdash; Jari Roomer</figcaption>
</figure>




